title: Master Services Agreement
summary: Dalil Technology LLC ("Provider") and Acme Corporation ("Client")
meta: | type: contract | ref: MSA-2026-0188 | effective: 2026-04-01 | status: Executed

section: 1. Engagement
text: Provider shall deliver the cloud platform, integrations, and support set out in
  Schedule A. Client shall provide timely access, data, and approvals as reasonably
  required for Provider to perform.

section: 2. Commercials
metric: Annual License | value: 96,000 QAR
metric: Implementation (one-time) | value: 38,500 QAR
metric: Total Year One | value: 134,500 QAR

section: 3. Service Levels
| Tier | Target | Credit |
| Critical | 99.9% uptime | 10% monthly fee |
| Standard | 99.5% uptime | 5% monthly fee |
| Response | < 1 business hour | — |

section: 4. Term & Termination
text: This Agreement runs for an initial term of twelve (12) months and renews
  annually unless either party gives sixty (60) days' written notice.
warning: Early termination without cause incurs the remaining term's license fees.

section: 5. Confidentiality
text: Each party shall protect the other's Confidential Information with no less than
  reasonable care and use it solely to perform under this Agreement.

section: 6. Signatures
